FHistoricalSection1995}}\n* {{cite web |last=Royal Australian Air Force |first= |authorlink= |coauthors= |title=No 1 Airfield Defence Squadron |work= |publisher= |date= |url=http://www.raaf.gov.au/adg/squadrons/1afds.htm |doi= |accessdate=9 July 2008 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20080627125655/http://www.raaf.gov.au/adg/squadrons/1afds.htm |archivedate=27 June 2008}}\n* {{cite web |last=Royal Australian Air Force |first= |authorlink= |coauthors= |title=No 395 Expeditionary Combat Support Wing |work= |publisher= |date= |url=http://www.raaf.gov.au/organisation/wings/395ecsw.htm |doi= |accessdate=9 July 2008 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20080524101147/http://www.raaf.gov.au/organisation/wings/395ecsw.htm |archivedate=24 May 2008}}\n* {{cite journal|last=Smith |first=Hugh |title=High time for the high-readiness reserve |journal=Defender |volume=XXIII |issue=2, Winter 2006 |pages=35\u201337 |publisher=Australian Defence Association |location=Canberra |year=2006 |url=http://www.ada.asn.au/defender/Winter%202006/High%20Time%20for%20the%20High-Readiness%20Reserve%20(Defender,%20Winter%202006).pdf |format=pdf |issn=0811-6407 |accessdate=15 July 2008 |url-status=dead |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20070829191344/http://ada.asn.au/defender/Winter%202006/High%20Time%20for%20the%20High-Readiness%20Reserve%20%28Defender%2C%20Winter%202006%29.pdf |archivedate=29 August 2007 }}\n* {{Cite book |last=Stanley |first=Peter  | author-link = |last2= |first2=| author2-link = |title=Tarakan: An Australian Tragedy |place=Singapore |publisher=Allen & Unwin |year=1997 |volume= |edition=First |url=http://www.allenandunwin.com/default.aspx?page=94&book=9781864482782 |doi= |id= |isbn=1-86448-278-8 |ref=Stanley1997}}\n* {{Cite book |last=Stephens |first=Alan  | author-link = |last2= |first2=| author2-link = |title=Going Solo: The Royal Australian Air Force 1946\u20131971 |place=Canberra |publisher=Australian Government Publishing Service |year=1995 |volume= |edition