{"title_page": "1975\u201376 Divizia A", "text_new": "{{Infobox football league season\n| competition      = [[Divizia A]]\n| season           = 1975\u201376\n| winners          = [[FC Steaua Bucure\u015fti|Steaua Bucure\u015fti]]<ref>[http://www.romaniansoccer.ro/divizia_a/tables/1975_76.shtml 1975\u201376 Divizia A]</ref>\n| league topscorer = [[Dudu Georgescu]] (31)\n| prevseason       = [[1974\u201375 Divizia A|1974\u201375]]\n| nextseason       = [[1976\u201377 Divizia A|1976\u201377]]\n}}\n\nThe '''1975\u201376 Divizia A''' was the fifty-eighth season of [[Divizia A]], the top-level [[association football|football]] league of [[Romania]].\n\n==League table==\n<onlyinclude>{{#invoke:Sports table|main|style=WDL\n|source=[http://www.labtof.ro/romania/1975-1976/liga1/ LT]\n<!--Team positions-->\n|team1=STE |team2=DIN |team3=ASA |team4=SSB |team5=PTM |team6=UCV |team7=BAC |team8=RES |team9=BIH |team10=FAR |team11=ARG |team12=JIU |team13=IAS |team14=RAP |team15=UTA |team16=SAT |team17=CFR |team18=UCJ \n\n<!-- Team qualifications here (defined below)-->\n|result1=EC\n|result2=UC\n|result3=UC\n|result4=UC\n|result5=BK\n|result16=REL |result17=REL |result18=REL \n\n<!--Team results here-->\n|update=complete\n|winpoints=2\n|win_STE=21 |draw_STE=9  |loss_STE=4  |gf_STE=79 |ga_STE=33 <!-- Steaua Bucure\u0219ti -->\n|win_DIN=18 |draw_DIN=8  |loss_DIN=8  |gf_DIN=68 |ga_DIN=35 <!-- Dinamo Bucure\u0219ti -->\n|win_ASA=17 |draw_ASA=4  |loss_ASA=13 |gf_ASA=48 |ga_ASA=42 <!-- ASA T\u00e2rgu Mure\u0219 -->\n|win_SSB=14 |draw_SSB=9  |loss_SSB=11 |gf_SSB=52 |ga_SSB=41 <!-- Sportul Studen\u0163esc Bucure\u015fti -->\n|win_PTM=14 |draw_PTM=9  |loss_PTM=11 |gf_PTM=54 |ga_PTM=52 <!-- Politehnica Timi\u0219oara -->\n|win_UCV=13 |draw_UCV=10 |loss_UCV=11 |gf_UCV=41 |ga_UCV=32 <!-- Universitatea Craiova -->\n|win_BAC=14 |draw_BAC=7  |loss_BAC=13 |gf_BAC=37 |ga_BAC=35 <!-- SC Bac\u0103u -->\n|win_RES=14 |draw_RES=6  |loss_RES=14 |gf_RES=39 |ga_RES=55 <!-- FCM Re\u0219i\u021ba -->\n|win_BIH